{"tid":2442576,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩岸專題：大陸封殺「綠地」鳳梨  助台打開國際市場","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T13:49:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b88ca4481f670a8d446f56b1d1f3bb7b8de832a6","tid":2442576,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/3JG75PHFTBCGPPOWCQCXY6QDEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2F3JG75PHFTBCGPPOWCQCXY6QDEE%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHQVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=ca4fdad5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2F3JG75PHFTBCGPPOWCQCXY6QDEE%2F&h=0a8b0272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/3JG75PHFTBCGPPOWCQCXY6QDEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩岸專題：大陸封殺「綠地」鳳梨 <br />\n助台打開國際市場<br />\n<br />\n大陸3月1日起以「截獲檢疫性有害生物（介殼蟲）」為由暫停鳳梨（港稱菠蘿）進口，引發台灣一場「鳳梨保衞戰」。有高雄果農稱，近日各機關團體在政府呼籲下大舉採購鳳梨，採購量足以彌補大陸暫停進貨的損失。有分析認為，北京刻意挑選對大陸外銷依存度最高兼集中於綠營長期執政四縣市種植的鳳梨，作為「懲戒」民進黨政府的「精準利器」，但事實上其象徵意義遠大於實際意義，亦難收令台灣南部農民「政治轉向」之效。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：藉「養套殺」逼台聽話<br />\n<br />\n大陸上月底突然叫停鳳梨進口後，台灣行政院宣佈成立「農產品國家隊」應對，呼籲各界認購土產鳳梨，更補助運費協助果商外銷，把鳳梨空運遠至澳洲等地。有「鳳梨達人」之稱的高雄市大樹區果農楊義子對本報稱，他十年前開始做外銷鳳梨，外銷比例近年高達七成，其中大陸是最主要的外銷市場。「大陸在完全沒有預警下拒絕鳳梨進口，台灣人一聽到後，各機關團體都向。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9uhTNhjKMOz4EuuyEeYE4OiaNOc=/2213x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BRSSIQD7UFF5TCKM4ACTX5PTV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9uhTNhjKMOz4EuuyEeYE4OiaNOc%3D%2F2213x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBRSSIQD7UFF5TCKM4ACTX5PTV4.jpg&h=56fd53cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣總統蔡英文親身到盛產鳳梨的高雄市大樹區，力挺農民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果農轟北京經貿政治化<br />\n<br />\n「鳳梨在大陸的銷售在2018到2019年最好，進口最多，所以有台灣農民到海南去種地，但種出來的品種跟台灣相差很大，所以大陸消費者還是喜歡台灣產的鳳梨，價錢也較高。」楊義子稱，他早料到長期依靠單一市場的風險，故此近年沒有再增加銷售大陸的數量，同時開拓其他市場。他相信大陸暫禁鳳梨進口是出於政治考慮，企圖令盛產鳳梨的嘉義、台南、高雄和屏東的四縣市農民不再支持民進黨，但他認為此舉難以奏效。「現在台灣人都很團結，目前定單下得比銷往大陸的還多。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然楊義子近年已分散投資，減少農場栽種鳳梨面積，但坦言害怕大陸。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n回顧近十多年，大陸進口包括水果等在內的漁農產品，一直就離不開政治問題。早在陳水扁執政時期，時任國民黨主席連戰在2005年4月歷史性首次訪問大陸，同年8月起大陸對包括鳳梨、椰子、蓮霧、番荔枝（釋迦）等15種台灣產水果實施零關稅，翌年又新增19類漁農產品享同等優惠。馬英九上台後，兩岸在2010年簽署《經濟合作架構協議》（ECFA），大陸再給予台灣18個稅項農漁產品零關稅優惠，擴大台灣農漁產品進口，試圖籠絡民進黨支持者較多的南部選民。<br />\n<br />\n根據台灣行政院農委會統計，逾兩百項漁農和林業產品中，當中鳳梨、釋迦、蓮霧、柚子、石斑和合板六類產品，去年出口對大陸。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AdDnDgSSUvRrK9JC_0prcggeh1U=/1320x1133/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5OQZP2MRXBAZLCCUGLOBUSR4UU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAdDnDgSSUvRrK9JC_0prcggeh1U%3D%2F1320x1133%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5OQZP2MRXBAZLCCUGLOBUSR4UU.jpg&h=965617bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日本電視台安排美女主持田中瞳試食鳳梨，被網民大讚可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VG-3hKj0K7GYDnYkxhBNKPaxmeU=/1968x1256/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DH63M6ASJVFRHKKQ7JTL2ZHZ2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVG-3hKj0K7GYDnYkxhBNKPaxmeU%3D%2F1968x1256%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDH63M6ASJVFRHKKQ7JTL2ZHZ2A.jpg&h=2390904e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日本首相輔佐官木原稔（中）與駐日副代表蔡明耀（左），參觀食品展時稱要帶顆台灣鳳梨給首相菅義偉品嚐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Eb-BFFPomuoA5Nlz8NqBxd6PjC4=/686x393/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E6AS5P2QHFF3VMFYZZLXNGPUSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEb-BFFPomuoA5Nlz8NqBxd6PjC4%3D%2F686x393%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE6AS5P2QHFF3VMFYZZLXNGPUSU.jpg&h=e65e7004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣行政院長蘇貞昌早前公佈成立農產品國家隊，揚言不會讓農民吃虧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綠營順時勢 免墮政治陷阱<br />\n<br />\n東亞國際關係學者、東京大學。。。。。。。我們就繼續溝通盡快解決這個技術性問題，沒有陷入北京設下的陷阱。」<br />\n<br />\n林泉忠分析，大陸難以在現階段把打擊面從鳳梨再擴至其他台灣產品，最後頗大機會是「擇時而退」，撤回對鳳梨的「臨時」禁令。「除非大陸要正式啟動實施對台灣的經濟封鎖，以武促統。但這次向鳳梨出招明顯是效果不佳，沒有打中民進黨痛處。」他指國際輿論近日都關注這場風波，批評大陸又再打壓台灣；民進黨政府因應事件更積極為農產品開拓更多元化的市場，其中在2011年大地震獲台灣大筆賑災捐款的日本，今年從台灣進口的鳳梨<br />\n將由去年2,144噸大增至全年逾6,000噸，台日關係更趨緊密，這都是北京並不樂見的「反效果」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VWvSsC1aRXVXQVKUKDMKSTHPeKE=/745x617/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3V4JDZHY7JCBRPRNUFQHW3RAOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVWvSsC1aRXVXQVKUKDMKSTHPeKE%3D%2F745x617%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3V4JDZHY7JCBRPRNUFQHW3RAOA.jpg&h=bcc5d352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5Qsxilkt7rxKdP6FFKpK46pdYlw=/969x408/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H5ZRBSRRPZA3NNKXY3OCFY5BTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5Qsxilkt7rxKdP6FFKpK46pdYlw%3D%2F969x408%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH5ZRBSRRPZA3NNKXY3OCFY5BTE.jpg&h=896ee886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GXgWxh8SWfKsiuQRTFrpYvWQh_4=/1407x2193/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JRHZVIKCT5EMJIPDL4GMJUQMDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGXgWxh8SWfKsiuQRTFrpYvWQh_4%3D%2F1407x2193%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJRHZVIKCT5EMJIPDL4GMJUQMDE.jpg&h=2671a0d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce7b5e831ad8613577d5d9e50c0e7d0e5104f854","tid":2442576,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"食左台灣鳳梨，好正好食，個心都食得，一定會再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f6d7da9b374ca61790b57141ae8cf53c3fb6fc","tid":2442576,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"香港竟然仲可以入口台灣鳳梨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪可以話一國兩制未死得曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6538b937d8c63a42b350c0db7d13cea0a3e5ffa","tid":2442576,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"Hitomi唔同咗樣？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f32405a53eec0b72239b3cd46d4c3b4eea9bb0","tid":2442576,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"支那搞到台灣啲菠蘿貴哂，又贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那狗食番支那野咪好囉"},{"pid":"dfbd8f2775ab9e5c7bb8411162989d0b6efe7c93","tid":2442576,"uid":15830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"結果班農民咪開始諗點賣貨去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4288580b8f743e2845265d0cdb1afe9f308e798b","tid":2442576,"uid":104035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:46:47.000Z","msg":"支那冇啦啦幫咗台灣農業做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班戰狼傻閪真係弱智唔係扮架喎"},{"pid":"fd6fd7b53b265b8c7a8ee2b7b15806ba4309b3ee","tid":2442576,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"支那制裁邊個邊個就行運<img src=\"/as